{"tid":1089090,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似新一代 iPhone 機身設計流出，穿孔屏+五同鏡頭很 Android！","createTime":"2019-04-02T13:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T18:01:11.000Z","uid":50534,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79fbf2acc0bc1b779ebfb3531ff4e62cdb108496","tid":1089090,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/04/02/iphone-2020-design-leaked/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F04%2F02%2Fiphone-2020-design-leaked%2F&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=ae0e11d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/04/02/iphone-2020-design-leaked/</a><br />\n關於今年新一代 iPhone (暫名 iPhone XI) 的消息現時網上漸漸增多，日前我們看過 iPhone XI 的工程設計圖片。現在，著名爆料達人 Ben Geskin 再發出了一張「iPhone 2020」的設計草圖。雖然設計草圖僅僅是由簡單的線條勾勒出來，但是關鍵的信息都得到了體現，而且跟過往的消息很吻合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從設計圖紙中看出「iPhone 2020」的正面將採用四邊等寬全面屏設計，屏幕的左上角是類似於Samsung S10+ 的「藥丸形」穿孔屏，在孔中放置了鏡頭以及傳感器。另外，屏幕上方位未為聽筒。<br />\n<br />\n在 Twitter 上觀看圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBen Geskin<br />\n@VenyaGeskin1<br />\n iPhone 2020: Exclusive First Look<br />\n1,898<br />\n下午4:09 - 2019年4月1日<br />\n358 人正在談論此話題<br />\nTwitter 廣告資訊與隱私<br />\n至於背面的設計就有些奇怪了，在「iPhone 2020」的背面中部依然是熟悉的 Apple 標誌，但是左上角的鏡頭採用了類似華為 Mate20 系列的「五同」設計，將鏡頭排列成一個方形，裡面似乎還有著一顆別的傳感器。<br />\n<br />\n考慮設計圖張貼的日期剛好是愚人節，設計圖中的 iPhone 又有點醜，可信度即時下降了不少。現在距離「iPhone 2020」發佈還有一大段時間，預測還太早了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://twitter.com/VenyaGeskin1/status/1112628108216205312/photo/1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVenyaGeskin1%2Fstatus%2F1112628108216205312%2Fphoto%2F1&h=e31744f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/iphone-xi-concept-fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fiphone-xi-concept-fb.jpg&h=9aebc2d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d4d745ce7b4c0e5d6309fc7203ab5f9d70cf73a","tid":1089090,"uid":40470,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"同理<br />\n<br />\n同一件事<br />\n<br />\n靚仔做就型<br />\n<br />\n毒撚做就柒<br />\n<br />\n利申：apple不是毒撚"},{"pid":"2388086c5f7ab07bd554aa8f9e3dd674c0d4803e","tid":1089090,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚闊"},{"pid":"1235ad4c1bc5361e27e4ae9ef86e6daea434cda3","tid":1089090,"uid":89514,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:02:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a745163f4af5f998e4caedaa0c246fd1761c342","tid":1089090,"uid":99473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"Iphone 習"},{"pid":"afdef48036dc3223f4974fa5a6e30cdb21e929a9","tid":1089090,"uid":46560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"年都未知咩樣喎，2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031e8e07af3f36bf1592cfb0f02c009b9b2d32c0","tid":1089090,"uid":46560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afdef48036dc3223f4974fa5a6e30cdb21e929a9","tid":1089090,"uid":46560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"年都未知咩樣喎，2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"今年"},{"pid":"5f7f1eb2fec89659a3e9af6fbf4d13c80c81f124","tid":1089090,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"又黎？<br />\nSE2仲玩唔夠？"},{"pid":"3888077ea9e2f229be8d7a9035a20a49b3b25478","tid":1089090,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c51f25aadfdd4fdc456eccea2f5277a994e5748b","tid":1089090,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"求其ran張圖又打稻草人"},{"